data.description: This new construction home features the popular Athens floor plan! Features include white kitchen cabinets w/beautiful granite counters, 4 piece stainless appliance package (includes refrigerator). A breakfast bar is great for quick meals! Family room has been extended & boasts a beautiful custom built gas fireplace! Easy care luxury vinyl plank floors throughout the main level, large master bedroom w/spacious attached bath! Laundry room w/lockers! Bonus storage area in garage. The full front porch is great for seasonal decorating! 16x 16 patio, Grade & hydroseed incl & 1 yr builder warranty!
